title: Christian Dior Revolution Top Handle Bag
description: Christian Dior Revolution bag in black grained calfskin leather. Featuring signature 'Dior' plaque at front to be used as handclasp slot, aged gold-tone hardware & a tall top leather handle. The magnetic flap opens to a front flat pocket and suede lining interior with multi patched pockets. Approx. dimensions: 25cm(L) x 16cm(H) x 6cm(D), 15cm handle drop & 55cm detachable wide leather shoulder strap drop, adjustable. Accompanied by Dior card (dated 04/2017), receipts, dustbag and box.
